{"tid":543563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一代傳奇】宜家家居創辦人逝世 終年91歲","createTime":"2018-01-28T15:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T12:26:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a0736e3cb7fb279cfdc0e771adc6f7cc6730b48d","tid":543563,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/222137_15a04f1fc74f9ecd78fcbefbd9b1341f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F222137_15a04f1fc74f9ecd78fcbefbd9b1341f.png&h=7aa9360f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在全球多國有逾400間門市的瑞典家具連鎖店宜家家居（IKEA），其創辦人坎普拉德（Ingvar Kamprad）在家中逝世，終年91歲。<br />\n<br />\n宜家家居發聲明公佈坎普拉德的死訊，指他在周六於斯莫蘭（Smaland）的寓所中安詳離世，並形容他是20世紀其中一個最偉大的企業家。<br />\n<br />\n坎普拉德出身農家卻是商業奇才，在1943年、亦即他17歲時創辦宜家，至今業務拓展到49國，以前年計總營業額約350億歐元（約3,400億港元）。坎普拉德雖是億萬富豪，生活仍然簡樸，外遊愛坐經濟艙，去餐廳亦會把糖包拿回家用，更愛在商店快關門才去掃平貨。<br />\n<br />\n坎普拉德早在1986年已卸下宜家行政總裁一職，在2013年退出董事會，同時把經營權交給兒子打理。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180128/57765041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57765041&d=9ZLfab60MJFe0WuPRHKg0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=70a690ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57765041&h=4a2d76fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180128/57765041</a>"},{"pid":"3c7c3e2715f3f7d5afbefb463743421c17be8660","tid":543563,"uid":51720,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"這就係生活享受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e965819ae1b044e207609ad7efc3ff4c6103793","tid":543563,"uid":49197,"like":142,"di